fields.description: The Tiguar yoga brace works as an effective aid for stretching exercises and helps to achieve the correct posture while performing yoga.

fields.name: Virtufit Gym Ball + Pump 65 cm
fields.highlight: Gymballs are one of the most common pieces of exercise equipment today, offering unlimited training options to increase strength, balance and stability.
fields.description: The Virtufit Gym Ball gives you a gentle workout with adapted load and is suitable for both rehabilitation and strength training. The training can be done at home, at the gym or at work, the ball can even be used as an office chair. Using the ball as an office chair can be particularly useful if you have back problems or are pregnant and want to improve your posture.

fields.name: Virtufit Yoga Block Black
fields.highlight: Wide range of applications
fields.description: The Virtufit Yoga Block is a handy tool that doesn't take up too much space in your gym bag, so you can practice whenever and wherever you want. The product can be used as an extension of your own body and provide support for various exercises.

fields.name: Virtufit Yoga Mat 3 mm 183 x 61 cm
fields.highlight: Smooth carpet from Virtufit with a wide range of applications!
fields.description: Virtufit's yoga mat has a wide range of uses and is suitable for yoga, pilates and strength exercises. The mat is also suitable for both amateur and advanced users.

fields.name: M-nutrition Keto Boost + Electrolytes 170 g
fields.highlight: Keto Boost is designed for a ketogenic diet to improve fat burning and ensure the necessary fluid balance. Keto Boost is suitable to support the increased need for electrolytes during the ketogenic diet, i.e. it has been equipped with natural fat-burning ingredients such as green tea powder and guarana extract. The product is best suited as part of a keto diet, but it can also be used by anyone else who wants to promote fluid balance and thereby optimise performance.
fields.description: Keto Boost + Electrolytes contains a comprehensive blend of ingredients that enhance fat burning while supporting a ketogenic diet by maintaining the body's fluid balance. Keto Boost contains 400 mg of green tea extract and 100 mg of guarana extract per serving, which, for example, boosts metabolism and increases the body's heat production. The fluid is managed by a potent blend of the key electrolytes, sodium and potassium. In addition, the product has been enriched with vitamin C, magnesium, vitamin B6 and vitamin B12.
fields.list1: Contains a blend of fat-burning ingredients and essential electrolytes
fields.list2: Enriched with extra vitamins and minerals
fields.list3: Tastes really fresh and dissolves easily

fields.name: Self Omninutrition Soy Protein 1 kg
fields.highlight: Self Soy Protein is the perfect protein supplement for those who demand vegetarian
fields.description: Soy protein is by far the best vegetable protein on the market today. It has a higher biological value than casein. Soy protein is perfect as a meal replacement or as a last meal before bedtime as it is a very slow-release protein. It contains only soy protein isolate, which means that all phytoestrogens are removed. This makes it suitable for both women and men.

fields.description: Smartshake Revive is easy to grip and carry thanks to the soft handle and rubber details. Revive is designed to match your personality with a variety of unique patterns and color combinations.
